timeline.bodyText:
nit: you should normally wrap JavaScript functions with $entry(); see e.g.



      rstudio/src/gwt/src/org/rstudio/studio/client/shiny/ShinyApplicationPresenter.java


        Lines 146 to 151
      in
      9ae3c31







                 $wnd.addEventListener( 




                       "beforeunload", 




                       $entry(function() { 




                          thiz.@org.rstudio.studio.client.shiny.ShinyApplicationPresenter::onClose()(); 




                       }), 




                       true); 





Some documentation on why this is done (primarily to ensure function is executed with an appropriate exception handler for GWT):
http://www.gwtproject.org/doc/latest/DevGuideCodingBasicsJSNI.html

